现在我已经完成了对项目的全面探索。项目有48个shadcn/ui组件可用，包括完整的表单、对话框、卡片、进度条、骨架屏等。现在我将提供完整的AI换衣应用实现方案。

---

# AI换衣应用详细实现方案

## 1. API集成方案

### 1.1 推荐的API服务

**首选推荐：Replicate - IDM-VTON 或 OOTDiffusion 模型**

**推荐理由：**
1. **易于集成**：提供统一的REST API，文档完善
2. **按量付费**：无需预付费，适合初创项目
3. **模型质量**：IDM-VTON是目前效果最好的虚拟试穿模型之一
4. **支持多种模型**：可以根据需求切换不同的试穿模型

**备选方案：**
- **Fashn.ai**：专注于时尚领域，但需要申请API访问
- **KlingAI/Kolors**：字节跳动的模型，适合亚洲人像

### 1.2 API调用流程

```
用户上传照片 → 用户选择服装 → 前端发送请求到Edge Function
                                      ↓
                            Edge Function代理请求到Replicate
                                      ↓
                            Replicate处理（30-120秒）
                                      ↓
                            返回生成的图片URL → 前端展示结果
```

### 1.3 Supabase Edge Function代理方案

由于CORS限制，需要通过Edge Function代理API请求：

**Edge Function设计 (`supabase/functions/virtual-tryon/index.ts`):**

```typescript
// 核心API调用逻辑
interface TryOnRequest {
  personImage: string;    // base64 或 URL
  garmentImage: string;   // base64 或 URL
  category: 'upper' | 'lower' | 'full';
}

interface TryOnResponse {
  id: string;
  status: 'starting' | 'processing' | 'succeeded' | 'failed';
  output?: string[];
  error?: string;
}

// Replicate API调用
const REPLICATE_API = 'https://api.replicate.com/v1/predictions';
const MODEL_VERSION = 'cuuupid/idm-vton:latest'; // 或其他试穿模型

async function createPrediction(input: TryOnRequest): Promise<TryOnResponse> {
  const response = await fetch(REPLICATE_API, {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: {
      'Authorization': `Token ${Deno.env.get('REPLICATE_API_TOKEN')}`,
      'Content-Type': 'application/json',
    },
    body: JSON.stringify({
      version: MODEL_VERSION,
      input: {
        human_img: input.personImage,
        garm_img: input.garmentImage,
        category: input.category,
      }
    })
  });
  return response.json();
}

// 轮询检查状态
async function getPrediction(id: string): Promise<TryOnResponse> {
  const response = await fetch(`${REPLICATE_API}/${id}`, {
    headers: {
      'Authorization': `Token ${Deno.env.get('REPLICATE_API_TOKEN')}`,
    }
  });
  return response.json();
}
```

**需要的环境变量：**
- `REPLICATE_API_TOKEN`：Replicate API密钥

### 1.4 前端React Query集成

```typescript
// hooks/useTryOn.ts
import { useMutation, useQuery } from '@tanstack/react-query';
import { supabase } from '@/lib/supabase';

export function useTryOn() {
  return useMutation({
    mutationFn: async (data: TryOnRequest) => {
      const { data: result, error } = await supabase.functions.invoke('virtual-tryon', {
        body: data
      });
      if (error) throw error;
      return result;
    }
  });
}

export function useTryOnStatus(predictionId: string | null) {
  return useQuery({
    queryKey: ['tryon-status', predictionId],
    queryFn: async () => {
      const { data, error } = await supabase.functions.invoke('virtual-tryon-status', {
        body: { id: predictionId }
      });
      if (error) throw error;
      return data;
    },
    enabled: !!predictionId,
    refetchInterval: (data) => 
      data?.status === 'succeeded' || data?.status === 'failed' ? false : 2000
  });
}
```

---

## 2. 应用架构设计

### 2.1 页面结构和路由规划

```
/                     # 首页 - 品牌展示 + 快速开始入口
/try-on               # 核心换衣页面
/gallery              # 用户历史记录/作品集
/wardrobe             # 服装库浏览
```

### 2.2 组件层级设计

```
App
├── Layout (全局布局)
│   ├── Header (导航栏)
│   │   ├── Logo
│   │   ├── Navigation
│   │   └── UserMenu (可选)
│   ├── Main (内容区)
│   │   └── <Outlet /> (路由出口)
│   └── Footer
│
├── Pages
│   ├── HomePage
│   │   ├── HeroSection
│   │   ├── FeatureShowcase
│   │   └── CTASection
│   │
│   ├── TryOnPage (核心页面)
│   │   ├── TryOnWorkspace
│   │   │   ├── ImageUploadPanel
│   │   │   │   ├── PhotoDropzone
│   │   │   │   ├── PhotoPreview
│   │   │   │   └── PhotoControls
│   │   │   ├── GarmentSelectorPanel
│   │   │   │   ├── GarmentCategoryTabs
│   │   │   │   ├── GarmentGrid
│   │   │   │   └── GarmentUploader
│   │   │   └── ResultPanel
│   │   │       ├── ResultPreview
│   │   │       ├── ProcessingIndicator
│   │   │       └── ResultActions
│   │   └── TryOnHistory (侧边栏/抽屉)
│   │
│   ├── GalleryPage
│   │   ├── GalleryFilters
│   │   └── GalleryGrid
│   │
│   └── WardrobePage
│       ├── WardrobeCategories
│       └── WardrobeItems
│
└── Shared Components
    ├── ImageCompare (对比滑块)
    ├── ImageCropper (裁剪组件)
    ├── LoadingOverlay
    └── ErrorBoundary
```

### 2.3 状态管理方案 (Zustand)

```typescript
// store/tryOnStore.ts
import { create } from 'zustand';
import { persist } from 'zustand/middleware';

interface TryOnImage {
  id: string;
  url: string;
  file?: File;
  type: 'person' | 'garment' | 'result';
}

interface TryOnState {
  // 图片状态
  personImage: TryOnImage | null;
  garmentImage: TryOnImage | null;
  resultImage: TryOnImage | null;

  // 处理状态
  isProcessing: boolean;
  processingProgress: number;
  predictionId: string | null;

  // 历史记录
  history: Array<{
    id: string;
    personImage: string;
    garmentImage: string;
    resultImage: string;
    createdAt: Date;
  }>;

  // Actions
  setPersonImage: (image: TryOnImage | null) => void;
  setGarmentImage: (image: TryOnImage | null) => void;
  setResultImage: (image: TryOnImage | null) => void;
  setProcessing: (isProcessing: boolean) => void;
  setProgress: (progress: number) => void;
  setPredictionId: (id: string | null) => void;
  addToHistory: (item: Omit<TryOnState['history'][0], 'id' | 'createdAt'>) => void;
  clearWorkspace: () => void;
}

export const useTryOnStore = create<TryOnState>()(
  persist(
    (set, get) => ({
      personImage: null,
      garmentImage: null,
      resultImage: null,
      isProcessing: false,
      processingProgress: 0,
      predictionId: null,
      history: [],

      setPersonImage: (image) => set({ personImage: image }),
      setGarmentImage: (image) => set({ garmentImage: image }),
      setResultImage: (image) => set({ resultImage: image }),
      setProcessing: (isProcessing) => set({ isProcessing }),
      setProgress: (progress) => set({ processingProgress: progress }),
      setPredictionId: (id) => set({ predictionId: id }),

      addToHistory: (item) => set((state) => ({
        history: [
          {
            ...item,
            id: crypto.randomUUID(),
            createdAt: new Date(),
          },
          ...state.history,
        ].slice(0, 50) // 保留最近50条
      })),

      clearWorkspace: () => set({
        personImage: null,
        garmentImage: null,
        resultImage: null,
        isProcessing: false,
        processingProgress: 0,
        predictionId: null,
      }),
    }),
    {
      name: 'tryon-storage',
      partialize: (state) => ({ history: state.history }),
    }
  )
);

// store/wardrobeStore.ts
interface GarmentCategory {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  nameZh: string;
}

interface Garment {
  id: string;
  name: string;
  imageUrl: string;
  category: string;
  brand?: string;
}

interface WardrobeState {
  categories: GarmentCategory[];
  garments: Garment[];
  selectedCategory: string | null;
  searchQuery: string;

  setSelectedCategory: (category: string | null) => void;
  setSearchQuery: (query: string) => void;
  filteredGarments: () => Garment[];
}

export const useWardrobeStore = create<WardrobeState>((set, get) => ({
  categories: [
    { id: 'upper', name: 'Tops', nameZh: '上装' },
    { id: 'lower', name: 'Bottoms', nameZh: '下装' },
    { id: 'dress', name: 'Dresses', nameZh: '连衣裙' },
    { id: 'outerwear', name: 'Outerwear', nameZh: '外套' },
  ],
  garments: [],
  selectedCategory: null,
  searchQuery: '',

  setSelectedCategory: (category) => set({ selectedCategory: category }),
  setSearchQuery: (query) => set({ searchQuery: query }),

  filteredGarments: () => {
    const { garments, selectedCategory, searchQuery } = get();
    return garments.filter(g => {
      const matchCategory = !selectedCategory || g.category === selectedCategory;
      const matchSearch = !searchQuery || 
        g.name.toLowerCase().includes(searchQuery.toLowerCase());
      return matchCategory && matchSearch;
    });
  }
}));
```

